    public class AccumulatingContinuousFunction<UD extends javax.measure.Quantity<UD>,UR extends javax.measure.Quantity<UR>>
extends ArraySampledContinuousFunction<UD,UR>
    A continuous function to accumulate the sum of input continuous functions. Accumulations made in rapid succession are batched so as to only lock for writing sparingly and minimize update events.
